WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
<v Narrator>Welcome to RestoreAssist. This guide shows you how to sign in to your account.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:12.000
<v Narrator>Navigate to restoreassist dot app and click the Sign In button in the top right corner.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:18.000
<v Narrator>Enter your email address and password, or use Google single sign-on for instant access.

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:25.000
<v Narrator>If you have two-factor authentication enabled, enter the code from your authenticator app.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:30.000
<v Narrator>You are now signed in to your dashboard, ready to manage inspections and generate reports.
